description: Open links to self-hosted GitLab instances in LabCoat Deep Links for LabCoat is a utility app that does one thing and only one thing: it allows you to open links to non-gitlab.com GitLab instances - for example, gitlab.gnome.org - in the LabCoat for GitLab app. Known issues: LabCoat opens but link does not load - Make sure you are signed in to an account on the Gitlab instance you are trying to access. LabCoat is unable to display anything from a Gitlab instance without a valid personal access token - even if the url you are trying to access is public on the web.
